From 04b077d8eb2fbd00afb55a08714871fa2a446ea1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 02:27:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] M411-M420: LOC+SP 13B bridge, preflight checks, fence
 ordering, timeout scaling

Following CCCL f984c90 (Extract first histogram-only pass in DeviceTopK
into its own kernel), this commit applies the same per-component extraction
and validation discipline across the LOC+SP stack for 13B model support:

=== M411: 13B model config ===

REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py:
  - Add 13B entry: n_layer=40, n_head=40, n_embd=5120
  - n_heads=40 gives sp_size=2 via GPU-type-aware grouping
    (2xA6000 as SP pair, H100 DP-only), same as 7B (n_heads=32)
  - Add 13B to argparse choices and cross-model analysis loop

=== M412: LOCSPGradientBridge configurable warmup + fence ===

loc_sp_bridge.py:
  - LOCSPGradientBridge.__init__ takes warmup_steps parameter
    (was hardcoded 512, now reads desloc.warmup from config)
  - should_sync() adds Kx<=1 fast path (standard DDP never skips)
  - post_backward_reduce() calls fence_all_sp_handles() before
    AllReduce to drain inflight A2A ops (prevents NCCL stream conflict
    on heterogeneous GPUs where A6000 A2A lags behind H100)
  - create_loc_sp_wrapper() validates n_heads % sp_size == 0
  - state_dict/load_state_dict extended with sync/skip counters

=== M413: all_to_all LOC group routing ===

all_to_all.py:
  - _resolve_group() checks is_loc_enabled() and routes through
    LOC peer group when DP-group index matches a LOC group
  - Add head_dim>0 assertion for 13B config validation

=== M414: sp_dp_registry timeout scaling ===

sp_dp_registry.py:
  - Add effective_timeout_ms() that scales base timeout by 1.5x
    for heterogeneous and 2.0x for LOC-enabled configurations
  - _drain_threshold() returns HALF high-water for LOC
  - fence_all_sp_handles() uses effective_timeout_ms() as default

=== M415: sp_compat preflight memory check ===

sp_compat.py:
  - preflight_memory_check() estimates per-GPU memory requirement
    before any NCCL initialization (fail-fast instead of OOM mid-train)

=== M416: init_sp 13B preflight integration ===

init_sp.py:
  - _estimate_param_billions() maps model_size string to param count
  - init_autosp() calls preflight_memory_check() before group init

=== M417: sp_compile LOC-aware validation pass ===

sp_compile.py:
  - pass_validate_loc_shapes() checks A2A node metadata shapes
    against sp_size when LOC is enabled
  - Inserted into AUTOSP_PASSES between propagate_shapes and canonicalize

=== M418: double_buffer_a2a memory guard ===

double_buffer_a2a.py:
  - allocate() checks buffer size against 30% of free GPU memory

=== M419: hetero_mesh BW table ===

hetero_mesh.py:
  - Add B100/B200 entries to bandwidth lookup table

=== M420: sp_histogram model-scale bin count ===

sp_histogram.py:
  - SPHistogramKernel.__init__ takes model_scale parameter

All files: zero docstrings, zero hash comments.

Signed-off-by: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
